Description: StereoLabs ZED SDK for NVIDIA Jetson platforms
 The ZED SDK provides advanced computer vision and depth sensing capabilities
 for StereoLabs ZED cameras on NVIDIA Jetson devices.
 .
 This package includes:
  - ZED SDK libraries and headers
  - Python bindings (pyzed)
  - Development tools and samples
  - AI model optimizer for Jetson NPU/DLA
  - ZED Media Server for streaming
 .
 Platform: NVIDIA Jetson (JetPack 6.0 / L4T 36.3)
